# Theme (`themes/omid-dev`)

Follow `AGENTS.md` for project context.

- Layouts: Go templates in `layouts/`; extend partials rather than duplicating markup.
- CSS: modular files under `assets/css/`; use tokens from `core/` and existing components.
- i18n: string files in `i18n/*.yaml` for all three languages when adding UI text.
- RTL: test `fa` layout when changing navigation, prose, or flex/grid styles.
- Shortcodes: add or edit in `layouts/shortcodes/`.
- After changes, run `hugo --minify` and fix template errors before finishing.
